ement-row-name\">ISACA Risk Event</h4><p class=\"engagement-row-meta\">Netherlands<!-- --> · <!-- -->Cybersecurity considerations for AI systems</p></div><a class=\"engagement-row-link\" href=\"/speaking/isaca-risk-event-2023\">Watch →</a></div><div class=\"engagement-row\"><span class=\"engagement-row-year\">2023</span><div class=\"engagement-row-details\"><h4 class=\"engagement-row-name\">World Summit AI</h4><p class=\"engagement-row-meta\">Amsterdam<!-- --> · <!-- -->AI security and governance</p></div><a class=\"engagement-row-link\" href=\"/speaking/world-summit-ai-2023\">Details →</a></div><div class=\"engagement-row\"><span class=\"engagement-row-year\">2023</span><div class=\"engagement-row-details\"><h4 class=\"engagement-row-name\">Economist Metaverse Summit</h4><p class=\"engagement-row-meta\">Virtual<!-- --> · <!-- -->Securing the metaverse</p></div><a class=\"engagement-row-link\" href=\"/speaking/economist-impact-metaverse-summit-2023\">Details →</a></div></div><div class=\"expertise-cta\"><a class=\"view-all-link\" href=\"/speaking\">View all speaking engagements →</a></div><div class=\"speaking-cta-box\"><p class=\"speaking-cta-text\">Interested in having Arnaud speak at your event?</p><a href=\"mailto:arnaud@arnaudwiehe.com?subject=Speaking Inquiry\" class=\"speaking-cta-button\">Check Availability →</a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"writing\" class=\"articles-section\"><div class=\"section-inner\"><div class=\"section-header\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">Selected Writing</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle\">Thoughts on AI governance, cybersecurity leadership, and emerging technologies.</p></div><div class=\"articles-list\"><a class=\"article-list-item\" href=\"/articles/ncsc-vibe-coding-safeguards\"><div class=\"article-list-meta\"><span class=\"article-list-date\">April 8, 2026</span><span class=\"article-list-category\">Article</span></div><h3 class=\"article-list-title\">NCSC on Vibe Coding Safeguards: The Real Risk Is Control, Not Code</h3><p class=\"article-list-excerpt\">The NCSC&#x27;s clear signal to security leaders: AI-generated &quot;vibe coding&quot; is inevitable. The question isn&#x27;t whether to adopt it, but how to control it before it scales insecurity across your organization.</p><span class=\"article-list-cta\">Read article →</span></a><a class=\"article-list-item\" href=\"/articles/ai-governance-journey\"><div class=\"article-list-meta\"><span class=\"article-list-date\">April 7, 2026</span><span class=\"article-list-category\">Article</span></div><h3 class=\"article-list-title\">The AI Governance Journey (It&#x27;s Not About a Checklist)</h3><p class=\"article-list-excerpt\">Stop treating AI governance like a spreadsheet exercise. Framework implementation is not a checklist—it is a transformation journey. And increasingly, it is a competitive differentiator.</p><span class=\"article-list-cta\">Read article →</span></a><a class=\"article-list-item\" href=\"/articles/iso-42001-compliance-final\"><div class=\"article-list-meta\"><span class=\"article-list-date\">April 4, 2026</span><span class=\"article-list-category\">AI Governance</span></div><h3 class=\"article-list-title\">ISO 42001 Compliance: A Practical Guide for AI Governance</h3><p class=\"article-list-excerpt\">In December 2023, ISO/IEC 42001 became the world’s first certifiable AI management system standard. Here’s what it requires, how it relates to the EU AI Act and NIST AI RMF, and what boards should ask before pursuing certification.</p><span class=\"article-list-cta\">Read article →</span></a></div><div class=\"section-footer\"><a class=\"view-all-link\" href=\"/articles\">View all articles →</a></div></div></section><section id=\"music\" class=\"personal-section\"><div class=\"section-inner\"><div class=\"personal-block\"><div class=\"personal-header\"><span class=\"personal-label\">Beyond Tech</span><h2 class=\"personal-title\">Cello da Spalla</h2></div><p class=\"personal-description\">Accomplished musician and in